<LanguageData>
  <FCP_Quest_Power_Armor_Building_Location.questDescriptionRules.rulesStrings.0>questDescription-&gt;A transmission from [asker_faction_name] has reached us through the static-filled airwaves. They've located a pre-war [facility] but can't get its 古老 technology operational. The facility likely contains valuable pre-war tech, but it's currently occupied by hostiles. Clear the area and help restore this piece of 老旧-world engineering to working order.</FCP_Quest_Power_Armor_Building_Location.questDescriptionRules.rulesStrings.0>
  <FCP_Quest_Power_Armor_Building_Location.questDescriptionRules.rulesStrings.1>questDescription-&gt;来自[asker_faction_name]的情报报告表明他们在荒地中发现了一个完整的战前[facility]。该建筑群仍然有电力，但自动化安全系统和袭击者使其无法进入。他们需要经验丰富的荒地操作人员来保护设施并使其休眠系统恢复正常运行。</FCP_Quest_Power_Armor_Building_Location.questDescriptionRules.rulesStrings.1>
  <FCP_Quest_Power_Armor_Building_Location.questDescriptionRules.rulesStrings.2>questDescription->来自 [asker_faction_name] 的优先信息：“我们发现了一些大东西 - 炸弹落下之前的[facility]。这个地方是 老旧 世界技术的 g老旧 矿井，但我们无法破解安全协议。帮助我们清除当前的占领者并重新激活这座战前创新的纪念碑。”</FCP_Quest_Power_Armor_Building_Location.questDescriptionRules.rulesStrings.2>
  <FCP_Quest_Power_Armor_Building_Location.questDescriptionRules.rulesStrings.3>questDescription-&gt;Urgent communication from [asker_faction_name]: A [facility] dating back to the 老旧 world has been discovered, still largely intact after all these years. The potential technological salvage is enormous, but hostile forces have claimed it as their base. Eliminate the threat and help restore this relic of civilization to operational status.</FCP_Quest_Power_Armor_Building_Location.questDescriptionRules.rulesStrings.3>
